 have changed between the initial recognition based on the input file
 and a postprocessing based on the final acell, rprim, and xred.
 These modifications are detailed below.
 The updated tnons, symrel or symrel have NOT been reported in the final echo of variables after computation.
 Such change of spacegroup, or magnetic point group might happen in several cases.
 (1) If spgroup (+ptgroupma) defined in the input file, but the actual groups are supergroups of these; 
 (2) If symrel, tnons (+symafm) defined in the input file, while the system is more symmetric;
